                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-880104481" class="vote-count">4</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-880104481" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="880104481">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/wsy2002755/">大士かっこいい</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar50 rating" title="力荐"></span>
                    <span>2015-01-07</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">生命中无所谓先天的意义。生命被生活过了，它才有意义。然而使之有意义都是你的任务。它的意义也只是你所选择的而已。</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="922698458">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-922698458" class="vote-count">1</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-922698458" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="922698458">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/irachex/">睡睡睡</a>
                    <span>2015-05-16</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">存在的概念讲得清晰易懂。自由与责任的部分一直是认同和信奉的。“不存在人性”的说法倒是刷新了某种潜意识的认知，以前总见别人谈人性，没有认真思考过人性是什么。</p>
        </div>
    </li>

        </ul>
</div>

        

<div id="comments" class="comment-list new noshow">
